                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 md:flex-row md:gap-1">
                        <div>
                            <img src="{{ asset('blog/articles/2024/emparis/chaud-montagne.jpg') }}" alt="montagne debut lever soleil" class="pointer-events-none">
                            {% include "app/pages/blog/components/photo-commentary.html.twig" with { focal: 85, apeture: 1.8, speed: '1/320', iso: 100 } %}
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <img src="{{ asset('blog/articles/2024/emparis/lac-reflet.jpg') }}" alt="reflet ciel sur lac calme" class="pointer-events-none">
                            {% include "app/pages/blog/components/photo-commentary.html.twig" with { focal: 85, apeture: 2.8, speed: '1/800', iso: 100 } %}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 md:flex-row md:gap-1">
                        <div>
                            <img src="{{ asset('blog/articles/2024/emparis/sunrise.jpg') }}" alt="premiere lueur soleil" class="pointer-events-none">
                            {% include "app/pages/blog/components/photo-commentary.html.twig" with { focal: 85, apeture: 2.8, speed: '1/2500', iso: 100 } %}
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <img src="{{ asset('blog/articles/2024/emparis/hommes.jpg') }}" alt="groupe hommes sunrise" class="pointer-events-none">
                            {% include "app/pages/blog/components/photo-commentary.html.twig" with { focal: 85, apeture: 2.8, speed: '1/2500', iso: 100 } %}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 md:flex-row md:gap-1">
                            <div>
                                <img src="{{ asset('blog/articles/2024/emparis/petit-lac.jpg') }}" alt="petit lac" class="pointer-events-none">
                                {% include "app/pages/blog/components/photo-commentary.html.twig" with { focal: 85, apeture: 2.8, speed: '1/2500', iso: 100 } %}
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <img src="{{ asset('blog/articles/2024/emparis/wide-lac.jpg') }}" alt="grand angle petit lac" class="pointer-events-none">
                                {% include "app/pages/blog/components/photo-commentary.html.twig" with { focal: 24, apeture: 2.8, speed: '1/2500', iso: 100 } %}
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <img src="{{ asset('blog/articles/2024/emparis/chemin.jpg') }}" alt="chemin prairie" class="pointer-events-none">
                                {% include "app/pages/blog/components/photo-commentary.html.twig" with { focal: 24, apeture:2.8, speed: '1/1250', iso: 100 } %}
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-12 border-t border-gray-200 flex flex-col gap-6">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Conclusion</h2>
                    <p class="mt-4">
                        Si vous avez l’opportunité de faire une randonnée au Plateau d'Emparis, je vous conseille
                        vivement de tenter l’expérience du bivouac au Lac Noir. C’est une aventure qui mêle solitude,
                        beauté naturelle et moments d’émerveillement.
                    </p>
                </div>
                {% include "app/pages/blog/components/data_technique.html.twig" with { duration: '2h20', km: 7.11, d: 741, altitude: 2444, isOnlyAller: true } %}
                <div class="mt-4">
                    <img src="{{ asset('blog/articles/2024/emparis/carte.png') }}" alt="carte rando" class="pointer-events-none">
                </div>
            </div>
            {% include "app/pages/blog/components/social_media.html.twig" %}
        </article>
    </section>
{% endblock %}

